## run make -C /etc/selinux/refpolicy/src/policy install
## Before switching selinux on along with the commands:
##

## Local policy development:
##        make policy

## Compile and install the policy:
##        make install

## Compile, install, and load the policy:
##        make load

## Filesystem labeling:
##        make relabel
##        make checklabels
##        make restorelabels
